Turn toward the bed and turn left into the sink.
Place the knife in the sink, rinse the knife, and pick it back up.
Place the knife on the sidetable to the right of the microwave.

high_descs: Go straight turn left then go straight turn left to the desk.
Take the knife from the table.

Turn around go straight head towards the sidetable near to the oven
Place the knife on the sidetable.

Pick up knife from the desk
